user_review: Really good Peking duck place! You need to call in advance to order the duck. You get four small plates of duck meat, a plate of crispy duck skin which you dip in a bit of sugar, a small plate of stir fried duck loin, duck bone soup, and white flour "tortillas" that you use to make delicious duck "tacos".We tried the meatballs, which were really good as well.
